edu.cmu.cs.stage3.io
Interface DirectoryTreeLoader

All Known Implementing Classes:
FileSystemTreeLoader, ZipFileTreeLoader, ZipTreeLoader
public interface DirectoryTreeLoader

DirectoryTreeLoader defines an interface for mechanisms that can load hierarchical trees of files, either from a filesystem, a network resource, an archive file (i.e. .tar), a compressed archive file (i.e. .zip), or some other storage medium.

Author:
Jason Pratt
